{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775868836978,"sessionID":"ses_285ff8cd3ffeYfvxMfbpOKDTUs","part":{"id":"prt_d7a07f455001P8y0SsJJW1ARCP","messageID":"msg_d7a07ebb10019YR51z3TC5MTjV","sessionID":"ses_285ff8cd3ffeYfvxMfbpOKDTUs","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_97c66669ee744d4bbb23fcc9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"python -c \"\nfrom agentcube.cli.main import app\nimport typer\nfrom typer.testing import CliRunner\n\nrunner = CliRunner()\nresult = runner.invoke(app, ['publish', '--help'])\nprint(result.output)\n\"","description":"Test CLI publish command help"},"output":"                                                                                \n Usage: kubectl-agentcube publish [OPTIONS]                                     \n                                                                                \n Publish/deploy an agent to the target provider.                                \n                                                                                \n Deploys the agent to AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or Kubernetes                 \n (Deployment + NodePort Service).                                               \n                                                                                \n╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│ --workspace       -f      TEXT     Path to the agent workspace directory     │\n│                                    [default: .]                              │\n│ --version                 TEXT     Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)    │\n│ --image-url               TEXT     Image repository URL                      │\n│ --image-username          TEXT     Username for image repository             │\n│ --image-password          TEXT     Password for image repository             │\n│ --description             TEXT     Agent description                         │\n│ --region                  TEXT     Deployment region                         │\n│ --cloud-provider          TEXT     Cloud provider name                       │\n│ --provider                TEXT     Target provider: 'agentcube' or 'k8s'     │\n│                                    [default: agentcube]                      │\n│ --node-port               INTEGER  NodePort (30000-32767)                    │\n│ --replicas                INTEGER  Number of replicas                        │\n│ --namespace               TEXT     Deployment namespace                      │\n│ --verbose                          Enable detailed logging                   │\n│ --help                             Show this message and exit.               │\n╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n\n\n","metadata":{"output":"                                                                                \n Usage: kubectl-agentcube publish [OPTIONS]                                     \n                                                                                \n Publish/deploy an agent to the target provider.                                \n                                                                                \n Deploys the agent to AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or Kubernetes                 \n (Deployment + NodePort Service).                                               \n                                                                                \n╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│ --workspace       -f      TEXT     Path to the agent workspace directory     │\n│                                    [default: .]                              │\n│ --version                 TEXT     Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)    │\n│ --image-url               TEXT     Image repository URL                      │\n│ --image-username          TEXT     Username for image repository             │\n│ --image-password          TEXT     Password for image repository             │\n│ --